NAME
     Example2 - EasySprite, DoubleBuffer, MousePosition, Oscillator

DESCRIPTION
     An animated sprite controlled by the mouse.

USAGE
     make
     example2

FILES
     example2.ca1 - CrackArt STLow picture file
     example2.ca3 - CrackArt STHigh picture file

